__e: When I said, "Jack and I," I felt this sudden wave of something.
They have come on a wave of terror, but we will push them back... Oh! Oh...
Multiple attacks over the years to come, countless lives are at stake.
I feel the power surge through me like an electric current rendering me capable of any feat of mind or body.
It's like this wave that crashes into you and pulls you out to sea, you can't you can't fight it.
And the sound came as a rising and falling wave across the water.
